nodes.text: Dorsk 83 was a Khommite male from Khomm. He was created to serve in the cloning facility where his forebears had worked, shortly before Dorsk 82 departed to train in the ways of the Jedi. It was his predecessor's hope that Dorsk 83 would also eventually become a Jedi Knight in the New Jedi Order, like he and Dorsk 81 had.
